  ListDialog:
  - DialogID: 0
    SentenceList:
    - "Huhu gi\xFAp ch\u1ECB v\u1EDBi (-_-). \xC0 qu\xEAn gi\u1EDBi thi\u1EC7u, \u0111\xE2y
      l\xE0 t\xF2a B, n\u01A1i th\u01B0\u1EDDng \u0111\u01B0\u1EE3c s\u1EED d\u1EE5ng
      l\xE0m gi\u1EA3ng \u0111\u01B0\u1EDDng cho c\xE1c b\u1EA1n sinh vi\xEAn. \u0110\u1EB7c
      bi\u1EC7t c\xE1c b\u1EA1n sinh vi\xEAn n\u0103m nh\u1EA5t \u0111\xE3 qu\xE1
      quen thu\u1ED9c v\u1EDBi ch\u1ED7 n\xE0y."
    - "Nh\u01B0ng c\u0169ng v\xEC th\u1EBF m\xE0 ch\u1ECB \u0111ang g\u1EB7p ch\xFAt
      r\u1EAFc r\u1ED1i \u1EDF \u0111\xE2y. B\xE0i to\xE1n m\xE0 em th\u1EA5y tr\xEAn
      b\u1EA3ng kh\xF3 qu\xE1. Em gi\xFAp ch\u1ECB nh\xE9. Ch\u1ECB kh\xF4ng mu\u1ED1n
      r\u1EDBt m\xF4n \u0111\xF3ng ti\u1EC1n h\u1ECDc l\u1EA1i \u0111\xE2u :(((("
    autoProgress: 0000
  - DialogID: 1
    SentenceList:
    - "Wowww. Em qu\u1EA3 l\xE0 m\u1ED9t thi\xEAn t\xE0i. Sau n\xE0y ra tr\u01B0\u1EDDng
      ch\u1EAFc ch\u1EAFn l\u01B0\u01A1ng s\u1EBD ngh\xECn \u0111\xF4."
